OL,5, Funding worth #9m to help relieve the  
OL,6, pressure on unpaid carers in Wales, has
OL,7, been announced.                        
OL,9,FThe Welsh government said the money,   
OL,10,Fover the the next three years, would   
OL,11,Fhelp full-time carers pursue hobbies,  
OL,12,Factivities or simply just read a book. 
OL,14,FThere are an estimated 400,000 unpaid  
OL,15,Fcarers in Wales.                       
OL,17,FCarers Wales welcomed the news that    
OL,18,Fwill help carers look after their own  
OL,19,Fhealth and well-being, especially after
OL,20,Fthe added stress of the Covid pandemic.
